herite CJ Edition</a>'s Gilded Netherite Material.</p>\n<h4>adds Material support for:</h4>\n<p>Gilded Netherite:&nbsp; this inculdes quivers, weapons, and gauntlets added by my main mod&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/expanded-combat\">Expanded Combat</a>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\nClick the banner to get the discount:\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/userofbricks\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/d94f7046-2c94-404e-a3dc-3a798daef810.webp\" alt=\"Bisect Hosting Promotional\">\n    </a>",
